item.title: Symptom Tracker
item.description: AMIA Symptom Tracker This was the demo application used for live-coding in the 4-hour Flutter workshop given at AMIA’s 2020 Virtual Clinical Informatics Conference. A total of 6 informaticians hosted this workshop.
